Title: Keep to fly, only with one wing
DateModified: '2019-02-27'
DatePublished: '2019-02-27'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/keep-to-fly-only-with-one-wing
SetInCountry: France
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Lystia Pramesti
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: "My dream start since 13 years ago. France, the one of my dream country that\
  \ i want to visit \"someday\". \nDay by day i still waiting that moment comes to\
  \ me. \nTadaaaaa, 2015 im divorced. I lost everything, but thanks God i have my\
  \ son. The day after divorce, i'm going down. No job, no house, no car, no money.\
  \ My dream?? What about my dream?? Lost... i have to let my dream go away. How i\
  \ can get my dream if i have no money. Ok! I lost my another wing to get that. \n\
  Now Almost 5 years, my life only for how to get better life, for me and my son.\
  \ \nStep by step I try to learn how I can back to fly even though only with one\
  \ wing. And yes, I prove it. I can fly with my one wing...yeah i can fly and France\
  \ waiting me please. I will come for you. Soon!!! And you are my first for another\
  \ second of my dream."
